### Step 1: Debounce Function

Create a debounce function to delay the execution of the autocomplete function.

```javascript
function debounce(func, wait) {
  let timeout;
  return function(...args) {
    clearTimeout(timeout);
    timeout = setTimeout(() => func.apply(this, args), wait);
  };
}
```

### Step 2: Autocomplete Function

Implement the autocomplete function to fetch and display suggestions based on user input.

